miniTwitter is a JQuery Plugin which put Twitter on your website. Website : [JQuery twitter plugin]: http://minitwitter.webdevdesigner.com/ "Put the twitter feed on your website".

You can find as well the [WordPress twitter widget]: http://minitwitter.webdevdesigner.com/ "Put the twitter feed on your WordPress Blog".

A lot of options can be modified like the username, the list, the query, the limit...

